Manga
A manga adaptation illustrated by Hoshina began serialization on Enterbrain's ''B's Log Comic service on December 5, 2017, and has been compiled into 16  volumes as of September 2025.
A manga adaptation of the Akuyaku Reijō wa Oshi ga Tōto Sugite Kyō mo Shiawase spin-off series illustrated by Ino Mamaru was serialized on the same service from January 5, 2021 to May 5, 2023. Its chapters were compiled into three  volumes released from July 1, 2021 to June 1, 2023.
