Visual novel
A visual novel adaptation developed by Operahouse was released for Nintendo Switch and Steam on March 21, 2024.
Anime
An anime adaptation was announced on July 4, 2025. It was later revealed to be a television series that will be produced by Studio Deen and directed by Takayuki Hamana, with scripts written by Yoshimi Narita, and characters designed by Majiro. It is set to premiere in January 2026.
Reception
The series ranked seventh in the shōjo/josei category in BookLive's Digital Manga Annual Ranking for 2019. In 2024, it was reported that the series had sold over 5 million copies.
